name: Band Logo Design
description:
I will design a logo for your band.

Just send your band name, genre, links to any recordings you have for inspiration, and any ideas you might have quoting your order reference to Midnightweave@gmail.com 

I will provide a range of versions of designs at various intervals for your input the final product will contain up to 3 hi res variants of a single design with a transparent background.
